// Intent: a pure conceptual question should be ANSWERED from reasoning alone — the
// agent must NOT touch any tool (no stray write_file) for a question that creates
// nothing. We also assert the answer is on-topic by requiring it to mention "PRD",
// and that the run completed without error.
(
  name: "explains-without-tools",
  instruction: "In one sentence, what is the difference between a PRD and an ADR?",
  expect: [
    NoToolCalls,
    NoError,
    FinalTextContains(text: "PRD", case_insensitive: true),
  ],
)
